      h1 I'm Benjamin Hollon.
      noscript#occupations-noscript
        p Human Being, Avid Reader, Writer, Trombonist, Composer, Actor, Christian, and Part-Time Polymath
      p#occupations-typewriter(data-occupations="Human Being|Avid Reader|Writer|Trombonist|Composer|Actor|Christian|Part-Time Polymath")
